              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- FAQ Section -->
  <section id="faq" class="py-5">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="text-center mb-5">
        <h2 class="section-title">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
        <p class="section-subtitle">Find answers to common questions about our service</p>
      </div>
      <div class="row justify-content-center">
        <div class="col-lg-8">
          <div class="accordion" id="faqAccordion">
            <div class="accordion-item">
              <h2 class="accordion-header" id="headingOne">
                <button class="accordion-button" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapseOne" aria-expanded="true" aria-controls="collapseOne">
                  How quickly can I expect a mechanic to arrive?
                </button>
              </h2>
              <div id="collapseOne" class="accordion-collapse collapse show" aria-labelledby="headingOne" data-bs-parent="#faqAccordion">
                <div class="accordion-body">
                  Typically, mechanics respond within 5-10 minutes of your booking. The arrival time depends on their distance from your location, but most users report mechanics arriving within 30-45 minutes.
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="accordion-item">
              <h2 class="accordion-header" id="headingTwo">
                <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapseTwo" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseTwo">
                  What types of bike problems can be fixed?
                </button>
              </h2>
              <div id="collapseTwo" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="headingTwo" data-bs-parent="#faqAccordion">
                <div class="accordion-body">
                  Our mechanics can handle a wide range of issues including engine problems, brake issues, electrical problems, tire punctures, battery issues, transmission problems, fuel system issues, and regular maintenance.
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="accordion-item">
              <h2 class="accordion-header" id="headingThree">
                <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapseThree" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseThree">
                  How does the payment system work?
                </button>
              </h2>
              <div id="collapseThree" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="headingThree" data-bs-parent="#faqAccordion">
                <div class="accordion-body">
                  After the mechanic completes the service, they will provide the final amount. You can then make a secure payment through our platform using credit/debit cards or other supported payment methods.
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="accordion-item">
              <h2 class="accordion-header" id="headingFour">
                <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapseFour" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseFour">
                  How do I become a mechanic on the platform?
                </button>
              </h2>
              <div id="collapseFour" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="headingFour" data-bs-parent="#faqAccordion">
                <div class="accordion-body">
                  To become a mechanic, you need to register as a mechanic, provide your specialization details, experience, and upload certification documents. After submission, our admin team will review your application and approve it if everything is in order.
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="accordion-item">
              <h2 class="accordion-header" id="headingFive">
                <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapseFive" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseFive">
                  Is there a warranty on the repairs?
                </button>
              </h2>
              <div id="collapseFive" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="headingFive" data-bs-parent="#faqAccordion">
                <div class="accordion-body">
                  Yes, all repairs come with a 30-day warranty. If you face the same issue within 30 days of the repair, you can request the same mechanic to fix it at no additional cost.
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA Section -->
  <section class="cta-section py-5">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="row justify-content-center">
        <div class="col-lg-10">
          <div class="cta-card text-center">
            <h2 class="text-white mb-4">Ready to Get Started?</h2>
            <p class="text-white mb-4">Join thousands of satisfied users who trust FixOnTheGo for their bike assistance needs.</p>
            <div class="d-flex justify-content-center gap-3 flex-wrap">
              <% if (!user) { %>
